	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Most games will work with a Game Genie or Action Replay as a "converter" though some games will require a cheat code to disable region lockouts. There are some games that will never work with a converter but these probably are fairly few. Mainly games that have extra hardware in them like Super Mario RPG, maybe also the Super FX due to timing issues. I'm not sure if I list of what you want exists.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


