	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Stop suffering. Buy an NTSC SNES or Super Famicom.
<br />
<br />Hard mods are mostly for people who know what they're doing and have technical expertize. 
<br />
<br />You will save yourself a lot of confusion and frustration, as an NTSC system will play all NTSC games without any kind of issue (SFC and SNES games as both use the same main board, just the casing of the console and cartridges are different)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


